# Position-only fixture for MeshLoaderTests.missingAttributes path: same
# quad geometry as quad.obj but with no `vt` lines and no `/vt` indices
# in the face list. A loader configured for position + UV should reject
# this rather than silently zero-fill the UV channel.
o quad_no_uv
v -1 -1 0
v  1 -1 0
v  1  1 0
v -1  1 0
f 1 2 3
f 1 3 4
